在setting.py中设置：
DEBUG = False

ALLOWED_HOSTS = ['*']


安装uwsgi命令:pip install uwsgi
在项目主目录下新建一个ini结尾的文件，写入配置内容
[uwsgi]
socket=127.0.0.1:8006
;http=127.0.0.1:8000
chdir =/Users/lixiangpeng/virtualenv/guliedu/GuliEdu
#指定项目的application
wsgi-file=GuliEdu/wsgi.py
#指定启动的工作进程数
processes=4
#指定工作启动的线程数
threads=2
master=True
#保存主进程的pid
pidfile=uwsgi3.pid
#设置uwsgi后台运行，uwsgi.log保存日志信息
daemonize=uwsgi3.log
stats = 127.0.0.1:9193

启动uwsgi服务器命令:uwsgi --ini [文件名].ini     停止uwsgi服务器命令:uwsgi --stop [文件名].pid

下载Nginx命令:pip install nginx

去/usr/local/etc/nginx下 ，复制nginx.conf.default为nginx.conf，在nginx.conf中添加内容:
    upstream GuliEdu{
        server 127.0.0.1:8006;
}
    server {
        listen       8002;
        server_name  localhost;
        location / {
            include uwsgi_params;
            # uwsgi_pass 127.0.0.1:3031;
            uwsgi_pass GuliEdu;
        }
        location /static{
            alias /Users/lixiangpeng/virtualenv/guliedu/GuliEdu/static;
        }
        error_page   500 502 503 504  /50x.html;
        location = /50x.html {
            root   html;
        }
    }
。。。。。
重启Nginx命令:sudo /usr/local/etc/nginx/bin/nginx -s reload
